quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  4,142,"Indeed the hypocrites (think that they) trick God, while He tricks them, and when they perform the mandatory prayer they perform it lazily to be seen by the people and they seldom remember God"
  4,143,"Indecisive in between that, not being of these and not of those. And whoever is misguided by God (according to His laws), you will never find a way for him"
  4,144,"You who believe, do not take the disbelievers as protectors instead of the believers. Do you want to give God a clear reason against you"
  4,145,"Indeed the hypocrites will be in the lowest level of the fire, and you will not find any helper for them"
  4,146,"except those who repented and straightened out and held on tight to God, and were sincere to God in their way of life, then they are with the believers, and God gives the believers a great reward"
  4,147,What would God do with punishing you if you are thankful and you believe? God is appreciative and knowledgeable
  4,148,"God does not like nasty talks in the public except by one who is wronged, and God hears all and knows all"
  4,149,"If you do good openly or hide it, or you excuse a bad deed, then God is pardoner and capable"
  4,150,"Those who disbelieve in God and His messengers and they want to separate between God and His messengers and they say: we believe in some and disbelieve in others, and they want to take a path between that"
  4,151,"they are truly the disbelievers, and We prepared a humiliating punishment for the disbelievers"
  4,152,"And those who believed in God and His messengers and do not make distinction between any of them, We will give them their reward. God is forgiving and merciful"